v0.1.0  2025-11-30
        Initial release.

        [Features]
        - pod_ok() for single-file POD syntax validation.
        - all_pod_ok() for recursive POD checking.
        - Exposed ignore list (@Test2::Tools::Pod::Ignore) for directory
          customization.
        - Duplicate filtering when scanning multiple locations.
        - Full Test2::API integration with proper context handling.
